    "But beyond this distributive point, an elemental ethics also opposes extractive logics that undermines the way these communities relate to water and the environment.",
    "Furthermore, the elemental ethics of MOSCAT and the Council reveals that injustices taking place within AI's value chain can not only undermine communities and humans but also the agency, needs and voice of the elements themselves.",
    "A third point present in both MOSACAT's and CAP's resistance concerns the lack of information regarding the availability of underground water.",
